text: Llanquihue () may refer to: *Lake Llanquihue, the second largest lake in Chile *Llanquihue Province, a province of Chile located in the southern Los Lagos Region *Llanquihue, Chile, a Chilean commune and city in Llanquihue Province, Los Lagos Region *Llanquihue River, a river in the commune of Panguipulli, southern Chile
title: Llanquihue
